description:
This week on Unqualified Anna and Sim sit down with one of the most decorated comedians in history, Russell Peters (Madison Square Garden, 02 London, Last Comic Standing)! They talk about life on the road, what it was like growing up Indian in Canada, and the time Russell punched someone during Scary Movie 2! After fearlessly taking on some wild deal-breakers, the gang calls Alex, who’s trying to navigate his dating life after constantly finding himself in the friend-zone, and Sarah, who doesn’t know what to do when her husband's avid guitar collecting becomes obsessive!

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
